snippet.textDisplay: I absolutely think the hair dryer is worth every penny. I purchased the air wrap, read the instructions, watched videos, and the result was not good, at all. I purchased the Coralle. Again, followed the instructions and I did not care for the technique or the final result. It's heavy, it did tug at my hair, not glide, I don't need another charging dock on my counter and 30 minutes of use doesn't work for everybody. I was drawn to the "less damage" but did not think this flat iron is anywhere near the retail value of $500. Not a fan.
